      <p class="style7">Emeril is a good cook on swing shift. He excels in production covering many $1500 shifts. His plates look good and receives many compliments on his quality. However, he is messy. By the end of his shift, you cannot find the floor. He seldom completes his sidework and leaves your graveyard cook with empty drawers and a dirty half-filled steamtable. Despite intense efforts to correct his bad habits, he seems to be set in his ways. </p>
