      <p class="style7">You hired Emeril two months ago and he has been given full training. For a while he had kept the line clean and organized. Now this problem has become a habit. You need a fast cook but to keep him, as is, you may lose a dependable graveyard and destroy the morale of the crew. You have heard comments like <em>“Since he gets away with it why should we work so hard?” </em> from your crew. </p>    </td>
